# Dtd
Dtd is a hobby project targeting to build a tower defense game with draft mechanics.

Tech stack: SFLM 3 (WIP) and C++17.

Nothing here yet

## Prerequisites

SFML dependencies need to be installed to the host system: https://www.sfml-dev.org/tutorials/2.6/compile-with-cmake.php

There is install_sfml_dependencies.sh for linux in the repository.

## Usage

Pull submodules first: git submodule update --init --recursive

make generate
make compile
make run
